2496                    lambda item: (item[0], item[1].to_dict())
2497                    if hasattr(item[1], "to_dict") else item,

2499                ))
2500            else:
2501                result[attr] = value
2502        if issubclass(SignHere, dict):
2503            for key, value in self.items():

2505
2506        return result
